Use the following command to compile the standalone password checking program. 

gcc -o password_program username_and_password.c username_and_password_checker.c utilities.c

Then use the command "password_program" to run the password checking functions.

This program will ask for a username and password and then store that username aand password as a file. The name of the file is the username and the contents ofthe file is the password. This file is stored in the username_file_directory directory.
